      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " and his mother's name was Naamah, an Ammonitess; which is repeated, that it might be observed as what was the leading step to his idolatry, and the means of his continuing in it: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and Abijam his son reigned in his stead; of whom there is a further account in the following chapter. ",
