        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Vat.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). Their occurrence twice so close together seems to shew that the compiler of 1 Kings was drawing from several sources, and that he copied ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Kings 14:21-24",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
