        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Kings 14:25-31",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " from another, which both contained the same piece of information about Rehoboam’s mother. Here as in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Kings 14:21",
        "children": []
      },
      {
